Output demo/copy-escape.gif
Set FontSize 20
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Padding 40

Type "./golem 'copy all .txt files from demo/fixtures/projects to /tmp/golem-demo-escape'"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 3s

# Destination path escape confirmation
Type "y"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

# Final copy confirmation
Sleep 1s
Type "y"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 4s
